[Well, this week's global update marks the beginning of officially reported cases with dates of onset of paralysis in 2019, confirming one case of WPV1 associated disease in each Afghanistan and Pakistan and one case of cVDPV2 (circulating vaccine-derived poliovirus) associated disease in Niger.

Interpretation: There is still significant circulation of the WPV1 in Pakistan and Afghanistan, and the cVDPVs are still circulating in Africa.

For a map showing the locations of cases of WPV and cVDPV, see http://polioeradication.org/polio-today/polio-now/. - Mod.MPP

