[Official confirmation of this newly reported case in the above media report can be found at the Pakistan End Polio website http://www.endpolio.com.pk/polioin-pakistan/polio-cases-district-wise-2019. The case had reported date of onset of paralysis on 15 Jan 2019, and was reported in Bannu, Khyber Pakhtunkhwa.

A map showing the districts of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa can be found at http://pamirtours.pk/maps/PD%20Maps/KPK_districts_map_2.jpg. Bannu shares a western border with both North and South Waziristan, both districts with high levels of vaccine refusal due to rumors about the vaccines. - Mod.MPP

